        "heading_line_2": "Sayonara to Smell.",
        "subtext": "Body odor is completely natural, but smelly clothes don't have to be. Instead of relying on constant washing to keep your clothes fresh, we engineered a fabric that actively prevents odor-causing bacteria from growing in the first place. The result? Clothing that stays clean, smells fresh, and rarely needs to see the inside of a washing machine.",
